description:
Pokemon.XY.S17E17.A.Rush.of.Ninja.Wisdom.HDTV.x264-CLDD.mp4


YTV (Canada) broadcast version.
Airdate: June 7, 2014


NOTE:
This is my last Pokemon cap. Someone else will need to step up and take over (next episode is June 14, 2014).


I am stopping Pokemon for many reasons.
1. I don't like Pokemon
2. Capping in general is taking up way too much of my free time, so why cap something I don't like? (I'm stopping other shows too)
3. It seems like a TON of Pokemon stuff eventually gets released on DVD.. and I've (usually) made it a point not to cap things that will be released to buy.


For the couple of people begging (sometimes more like nagging) me to continue, please stop. I wanted to quit Pokemon around episode 3, but held out this long.
